# Cargo Technician SOP

[bold]1.[/bold] Cargo Technicians are bound to the same rules as the [color=#1b67a5]Quartermaster[/color] regarding restricted crates;

[bold]2.[/bold] Cargo Technicians are [bold]not[/bold] permitted to order non-essential items using the supply account (such as cats, or clothing) without express consent from the [color=#1b67a5]Quartermaster[/color];

[bold]3.[/bold] Cargo Technicians are [bold]not[/bold] permitted to authorize non-departmental orders (such as a Medical Doctor asking for Insulated Gloves) without express permission from the [color=#1b67a5]Quartermaster[/color];

[bold]4.[/bold] Cargo Technicians must ensure resources brought by salvagers are distributed to the rest of the station.

[bold]5.[/bold] Cargo Technicians should ensure that at least one person is handling mail delivery, should the mail teleporter be turned on and functioning.
